high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn left to face the bathtub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap in the bathtub.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on for three seconds, then turn the water off and take the soap.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to face the toilet.
Place the soap on top of the toilet, next to the nearest bottle of lotion.
Back up, turn left, walk forward until at midpoint of tub, turn left to face the tub.
Pick up the soap that is in the bathtub.
Turn left, walk to sink, turn right to face sink.
Put soap in sink, fill the sink with water, empty sink, pick up the soap.
Turn left, walk forward, turn left, walk to toilet.
Place soap on front of toilet tank, standing up on its short end.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed bar of soap on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Pick up the bar of soap in the bath tub
Place the bar of soap on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Move a bar of soap from a tub to a toilet
